{"tid":818710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"舒貴人對腳好正啊","createTime":"2018-09-14T09:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T09:39:00.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9fb7777c8c84d714efbdad1f23ca06b000ffbf","tid":818710,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"這些機會不是屬於春望兄的<br />\n但千萬個舒貴人都抵不上一個純妃<br />\n純妃呢d女<br />\n太子黨都未必溝到<br />\n世上千萬個傅恆<br />\n而我<br />\n只係圓明園牛屎仔<br />\n換轉今日<br />\n只係食環莊臣碧瑤掃街仔<br />\n置地門外<br />\n千萬個純妃<br />\n要風得風<br />\n一隻包包<br />\n抵我十條命<br />\n上落s class<br />\n比呼吸更自然<br />\n而我<br />\n連搭1a都要俾人嫌棄<br />\n但每晚諗住純妃<br />\n哪怕只係御茶膳房試食隨時毒死既汁男<br />\n都願意用生命值硬接親近娘娘<br />\n過一日得一日<br />\n純妃真係好正"},{"pid":"12f2847999dc207d15337fdec6c52d1130d1400a","tid":818710,"uid":26711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黎"},{"pid":"f715c91768e8f6d35a2f615d3e0907663cea2cf2","tid":818710,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/173827_a78e4fc1e982359a38e8fc15da0b59f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F173827_a78e4fc1e982359a38e8fc15da0b59f7.jpg&h=f11b0f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7eb133dd2d5946004bf1582e9f0c1e2dedbb459","tid":818710,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}